      "content": "i just feel like i'm constantly performing. every single day is just... an exhausting act of pretending to be someone else so i don't cause friction. i'm so tired of fighting just to exist. it feels like the world was never built for me and i'm just wasting my energy trying to fit into a shape that doesn't exist.",
