    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so impossible though. like no matter how much i rest, the moment i wake up i have to put the mask back on. it's not just tiring, it's soul-crushing. i feel like i'm just waiting for a life that's never going to happen. i'm just so done with the struggle.",
