      "content": "but even the quiet places aren't enough. the world just won't leave me alone. it's like there's no version of this where i actually get to be peaceful and me. i look at everyone else just living, and i realize i'm just chasing a ghost. honestly, sometimes i think the only real way to stop the performance and finally be at peace is to just... stop everything. to just stop existing so the noise finally goes away.",
